					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7294131#post-3948440</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7294131/don-quixote-vs-classy-carlos#post-3948440</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 01 Sep 2018 09:04:11 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>keyii</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4420424</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I loved this. You make full use of the comedic potential of both characters and the writing is awesome. Glad that poor Agent Diego gets to go on an adventure — sounds like she's had a hard time! It's really nice that her character shines just as much as those of the tale's two main characters (Don Quixote and Carlos).</p> <p>My favourite line: &quot;I — I don't — hi. Hello. I just came in here to poop.&quot;</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
