						 <div style="font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; text-align: center;"> <p><a href="https://youtu.be/H2rd8rRQqe0">Here me now, O thou bleak and unbearable world!</a><br /> <a href="https://youtu.be/H2rd8rRQqe0">Thou art base, and debauched as can be!</a><br /> <a href="https://youtu.be/H2rd8rRQqe0">And a knight, with his banners all bravely unfurled --</a><br /> <a href="https://youtu.be/H2rd8rRQqe0">Now hurls down his gauntlet to thee!</a></p> <p><a href="https://youtu.be/H2rd8rRQqe0">I am I, Don Quixote!</a><br /> <a href="https://youtu.be/H2rd8rRQqe0">The Lord of La Mancha!</a><br /> <a href="https://youtu.be/H2rd8rRQqe0">My Destiny calls -- and I go!</a></p> </div> <hr /> <p>Wrote this for <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-oct-hub">SCP OCT</a> contest! <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3361">Classy Carlos</a> versus <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4028">Don Quixote</a>.</p> <p>And yes, this is basically &quot;Deadpool kills the Marvel Universe&quot;, except it's Don Quixote versus the SCP wiki.</p> <hr /> <div style="font-weight: bold; text-align: center;"> <h2><span>Like the article? Click <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/the-great-hippo">here</a> for more of <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/the-great-hippo">The Great Hippo's Skippos!</a></span></h2> </div> <div style="font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; text-align: center; font-size: 60%;"> <p><a href="https://youtu.be/TiAz_g2-H_E">...he lays down the melancholy burden of sanity...</a></p> </div> 
